onCreateViewHolder:- 

->create View object 
-> creATE hOLDER TO Store this view Object 
-> ViewHolder-just stores view so that it can be recyycled 


onBindViewHolder - 
->Binds data in views 
->this method provides a view holder & position 
-> Based on the position , it just binds the data into view which is 
then shown in the app 

Adapters 
->it adapts your data in a format that can be consumed by recycler view 
-> recycler view request data from adapater and provides the data  


